# Project Structure Guide
The project is organized as follows:

- [app/](mdc:app): Next.js App Router routes and layouts.
- [components/](mdc:components): Reusable React UI components (`.tsx`).
- [context/](mdc:context): React Context providers and hooks for global state.
- [lib/](mdc:lib): Shared utility functions and modules.
- [public/](mdc:public): Static assets served at root.
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts): Tailwind CSS configuration.
- [postcss.config.js](mdc:postcss.config.js): PostCSS plugins configuration.
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs): ESLint linting rules.
- [.prettierrc](mdc:.prettierrc): Prettier formatting rules.
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js): Next.js custom configuration.
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript compiler options.
- [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project overview and setup instructions.
- [.cursor/rules/](mdc:.cursor/rules): Cursor AI navigation rules (ongoing).